z-lib.org).pdf","target":"分布式服务架构：原理、设计与实战 by 李艳鹏 杨彪 (z-lib.org).pdf","line":52},{"title":"2021最新版Spring Cloud Alibaba从入门到精通全套超详细教程【附赠完整学习代码+笔记资料】_哔哩哔哩_bilibili","target":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Lb4y1r7Jk?p=2","line":54},{"title":"Fetching Title#28sx","target":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Lb4y1r7Jk?p=2#t=294.428725","line":55},{"title":"#^c85e1a","target":"#^c85e1a","line":57},{"title":"05:12","target":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Lb4y1r7Jk?p=2#t=312.863833","line":57},{"title":"JEE 以面向对象的 Java 编程语言为基础，扩展了 Java 平台的标准版，是 Java 平台企业版的简称。它作为企业级软件开发的运行时和开发平台，极大地促进了企业开发和定制信息化系统的进展。","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%20by%20%E6%9D%8E%E8%89%B3%E9%B9%8F%20%E6%9D%A8%E5%BD%AA%20(z-lib.org","line":63},{"title":"JEE 将企业级软件架构分为三个层级： Web 层、业务逻辑层和数据存取层","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%20by%20%E6%9D%8E%E8%89%B3%E9%B9%8F%20%E6%9D%A8%E5%BD%AA%20(z-lib.org","line":65},{"title":"所以尽管 JEE 支持 Web容器和 EJB 容器的分离部署，这个时代的大多数项目仍然部署在同一个应用服务器上井跑在一个 JVM进程中。","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%20by%20%E6%9D%8E%E8%89%B3%E9%B9%8F%20%E6%9D%A8%E5%BD%AA%20(z-lib.org","line":67},{"title":"团队的交流机制应该与架构分层交互机制相对应。","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%20by%20%E6%9D%8E%E8%89%B3%E9%B9%8F%20%E6%9D%A8%E5%BD%AA%20(z-lib.org","line":69},{"title":"479","target":"booknote/books-data/resources/(annots)分布式服务架构：原理、设计与实战 by 李艳鹏 杨彪 (z-lib.org).pdf/p26r91.850,166.320,379.360,344.990z2i(235cb7f4-2978-269c-8e8a-a23d71f6900f).png#center","line":71},{"title":"574","target":"booknote/books-data/resources/(annots)分布式服务架构：原理、设计与实战 by 李艳鹏 杨彪 (z-lib.org).pdf/p28r72.350,290.880,416.470,564.550z2i(21801944-3f10-6971-34a8-51d4204a974f).png#center","line":71},{"title":"SOA代表面向服务的架构，俗称服务化，后面所说的SOA、服务化、 SOA 服务化若没有特殊说明则指 SOA 。 SOA 将应用程序的模块化组件通过定义明确的接口和契约联系起来，==接口是采用中立的方式进行定义的，独立于某种语言、硬件和操作系统==，通常通过网络通信来完成，但是并不局限于某种网络协议，可以是底层的 TCP膺，可以是应用层的 HTTP，也可以是消息队列协议，甚至可以是约定的某种数据库存储形式。这使得各种各样的系统中的模块化组件可以以一种统一和通用的方式进行交互。","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%20by%20%E6%9D%8E%E8%89%B3%E9%B9%8F%20%E6%9D%A8%E5%BD%AA%20(z-lib.org","line":74},{"title":"要彻底理解 SOA 时代的服务化发展情况，我们必须理解 SOA 的两个主流实现方式： WebService 平日 ESB 。","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%20by%20%E6%9D%8E%E8%89%B3%E9%B9%8F%20%E6%9D%A8%E5%BD%AA%20(z-lib.org","line":76},{"title":"SOAP 协议通常是一种在 HTTP 或者 HTTPS通道上传输X岛伍数据来实现的协议，但是每个服务都要依赖中心化 Web Service 目录来发现现存的服务。","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%20by%20%E6%9D%8E%E8%89%B3%E9%B9%8F%20%E6%9D%A8%E5%BD%AA%20(z-lib.org","line":78},{"title":"647","target":"booknote/books-data/resources/(annots)分布式服务架构：原理、设计与实战 by 李艳鹏 杨彪 (z-lib.org).pdf/p30r48.630,171.170,436.600,403.550z2i(508d5bc7-8773-fbf6-f215-826f0c07ce25).png#center","line":80},{"title":"ESB是企业服务总线的简称，是用于设计和实现网络化服务交互和通信的软件模型，是SOA的另一种实现方式，主要用于企业信息化系统的集成服务场景中。 Mule 是企业服务总线的一个实现。","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%20by%20%E6%9D%8E%E8%89%B3%E9%B9%8F%20%E6%9D%A8%E5%BD%AA%20(z-lib.org","line":84},{"title":"611","target":"booknote/books-data/resources/(annots)分布式服务架构：原理、设计与实战 by 李艳鹏 杨彪 (z-lib.org).pdf/p32r60.400,402.530,426.880,597.030z2i(31a000e0-7d7c-dd86-1a8e-0c90e24811f7).png#center","line":86},{"title":"693","target":"booknote/books-data/resources/(annots)分布式服务架构：原理、设计与实战 by 李艳鹏 杨彪 (z-lib.org).pdf/p36r36.340,103.100,451.960,245.900z2i(482ebdc8-66a3-445a-0fd3-01660c16517d).png#center","line":88},{"title":"682","target":"booknote/books-data/resources/(annots)分布式服务架构：原理、设计与实战 by 李艳鹏 杨彪 (z-lib.org).pdf/p37r62.440,332.400,471.410,592.420z2i(129202c3-8dd0-a97c-d728-52cfe7f85bf6).png#center","line":89}],"blocks":{"#":[1,10],"#CAP原则":[11,16],"#CAP原则#{1}":[12,16],"#负载均衡":[17,20],"#负载均衡#{1}":[18,18],"#负载均衡#{2}":[19,20],"#微服务":[21,90],"#微服务#{1}":[23,90]},"last_import":{"mtime":1647100084301,"size":8332,"at":0,"hash":"8214650c2444a6e8cab6f7b85d235379fa5fe28db7b4dbd9f456e1ad9c74caa1"},"key":"微服务架构.md"},
